            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44281745">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">当年鲁迅看中国是“有病不求药，无聊才读书”，而今已经变了，无病却吃药，无聊亦不读书。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-24 23:17</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>当年鲁迅看中国是“有病不求药，无聊才读书”，而今已经变了，无病却吃药，无聊亦不读书。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
